 bandits. <br><br>Therefore, I would expect a fight if I am found snooping about. I tell you all this in the event I do not return in a timely fashion. I do not expect to find my folks on this island, but if there is one there who knows of, or may be responsible for their demise, I shall bring such vile scum to justice for his actions.<br><br>It is my intent to be on this vessel this eve as the Freeport chart master has claimed clear skies around dusk. I shall send message without haste upon my return.<br><br>Be well <br>Ayben&quot;<br><br>*Ayben checks his gear, and heads to the provisioner to gather supplies for his journey.* <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub5.ezboard.com/uayben.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ayben</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Kin</span><br>  Posts: 18<br> <font color=#330000>(6/20/02 9:23:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1614.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Journey</span><hr size=1> *Ayben once again enters the Great Hall. Seeing his original message has fallen under some newer ones, he takes a quill, and scribbles a quick note at the the bottom and replaces the message.*<br><br>&quot;Failte Clan! <br>The trip to the ship island was for naught. Just by the sight of the filthy curs that inhabit this place I was sure they would know nothing of parents, let alone be in the position to keep them hostage. My father was strong enough to lay waste to those bandits 10 times over. <br><br>I did however encounter someone on the boat that told me of High Pass. They told me of gnolls and orcs that terrorize this place. He gave me a memo to take there that would allow me to gain temporary residence. With this note I shall be heading off to help the battles against these orcs and gnolls. So, if ye need me, that is where I shall be.<br><br>Ayben&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=1614.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=1614.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1614.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=1614.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.threadControl?topicID=1614.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1614.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1614.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub5.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="theclanmacleargeneral">The Great Hall<option value="theclanmaclearfrm8">Inner Court<option value="theclanmaclearfrm6">Events<option value="theclanmaclearfrm5">Provisioner's Square<option value="theclanmaclearfrm4">Chi